WEBVTT

1
00:01:57.578 --> 00:01:59.413
OSAM GODINA POSLIJE

2
00:03:20.828 --> 00:03:21.704
Da.

3
00:03:29.128 --> 00:03:30.213
Neuspjeh.

4
00:03:30.296 --> 00:03:31.589
Nije.

5
00:03:33.507 --> 00:03:35.509
Oružje je u mojoj ruci.

6
00:03:36.385 --> 00:03:38.054
Mislila sam da ga imam.

7
00:03:40.473 --> 00:03:42.516
Oprosti, oče, uspjet ću sljedeći put.

8
00:03:42.600 --> 00:03:44.936
Ništa ne uzimaj zdravo za gotovo.

9
00:03:45.853 --> 00:03:47.438
Bog će ti to oduzeti.

10
00:03:49.357 --> 00:03:50.691
Je li Bog loš?

11
00:03:54.237 --> 00:03:55.321
Bog je pravedan.

12
00:03:59.075 --> 00:04:01.744
Gotovo si me sredio, zar ne, dečko?

13
00:04:22.181 --> 00:04:25.935
Bijelu kosu imam na tebe ili na mamu?

14
00:04:28.479 --> 00:04:29.814
Na svoju mamu.

15
00:04:29.897 --> 00:04:32.900
Ne mogu vjerovati da nemamo njezine slike.

16
00:04:32.984 --> 00:04:36.863
Sve je uništeno u požaru. Znaš to.

17
00:04:36.946 --> 00:04:38.781
Uspio sam samo tebe spasiti.

18
00:04:42.952 --> 00:04:44.662
Je li bila prekrasna?

19
00:04:49.959 --> 00:04:51.252
Bila je pametna.

20
00:04:53.838 --> 00:04:55.172
Poput tebe.

21
00:04:56.340 --> 00:04:59.135
Koliko sam pogodila?
-Sve.


22
00:05:01.596 --> 00:05:04.599
Znači da danas mogu u grad, točno?

23
00:05:07.393 --> 00:05:09.228
Nisi uspjela u preživljavanju.

24
00:05:10.897 --> 00:05:13.107
Prošla su tri mjeseca.

25
00:05:14.192 --> 00:05:17.612
Plus, upravo sam te super ošišala.

26
00:05:18.070 --> 00:05:19.197
Vjeruj mi.

27
00:05:21.115 --> 00:05:24.118
Prvo moraš proći sve testove.

28
00:05:36.339 --> 00:05:39.091
U redu. Osim uobičajenog,

29
00:05:39.175 --> 00:05:43.095
imam narudžbu za pet paprati, dva fikusa

30
00:05:43.179 --> 00:05:45.640
i columnea grandiosas.

31
00:05:46.599 --> 00:05:48.893
Gloriosas.
-Gloriosas.


32
00:05:50.019 --> 00:05:51.854
Vozim li danas Phoenix?

33
00:05:51.938 --> 00:05:54.857
Ne danas.
-Dugo nisam.


34
00:05:54.941 --> 00:05:56.526
Rekao sam ne.

35
00:06:00.571 --> 00:06:02.448
Znate, ili popustite povodac,

36
00:06:02.532 --> 00:06:04.784
ili će ga prije ili poslije pregristi.

37
00:06:19.173 --> 00:06:20.508
Idi s Hernandzicom.

38
00:06:25.137 --> 00:06:28.057
Vrati se do zalaska sunca.
-Hoću.


39
00:06:32.270 --> 00:06:35.481
Hej, Hernandezice.
-Hej, ljepotice.


40
00:06:43.906 --> 00:06:47.535
Leti, leti, ptičice

41
00:06:47.618 --> 00:06:50.830
Preko moćnoga mora

42
00:06:50.913 --> 00:06:56.586
Pjevaj, pjevaj, djevojčice
Iz svega srca za mene


43
00:06:56.669 --> 00:06:58.004
To je prekrasno.

44
00:06:58.671 --> 00:07:00.256
Ti si to smislila?

45
00:07:01.173 --> 00:07:04.093
Mislim da mi je to mama pjevala
kad sam bila mala.


46
00:07:04.176 --> 00:07:06.304
Taj prvi dio sve je što pamtim.

47
00:07:06.387 --> 00:07:08.222
Želiš li je posjetiti?

48
00:07:10.224 --> 00:07:11.893
Ali moj otac ne želi da...

49
00:07:11.976 --> 00:07:13.978
Neću mu reći ako mu ti ne kažeš.

50
00:07:18.024 --> 00:07:20.902
NADA

51
00:07:44.300 --> 00:07:46.802
VOLIM TE MAMA

52
00:07:51.307 --> 00:07:54.852
Leti, leti, ptičice

53
00:08:12.745 --> 00:08:15.498
Policija je izdala tjeralicu
za dr. Thomasom Hannimanom


54
00:08:15.581 --> 00:08:16.499
TRGOVINA ORGANIMA

55
00:08:16.582 --> 00:08:18.960
osumnjičenog da vodi
bandu trgovaca organima


56
00:08:19.043 --> 00:08:20.211
na području Detroita.

57
00:08:20.294 --> 00:08:21.128
ZA PRESAĐIVANJE

58
00:08:21.212 --> 00:08:24.423
Broj otmica u gradu alarmantno se povećao.

59
00:08:24.507 --> 00:08:25.841
Ovo je priča u tijeku.

60
00:08:25.925 --> 00:08:28.803
Javljat ćemo vam nove informacije.

61
00:08:28.886 --> 00:08:31.430
Sada pogledajmo prognozu za vikend.

62
00:08:31.514 --> 00:08:33.599
Dobro jutro. Ja sam meteorolog...

63
00:08:42.525 --> 00:08:44.986
Vucite svi! Pomozite mi!

64
00:08:46.070 --> 00:08:47.572
Zapela sam.

65
00:08:50.700 --> 00:08:52.118
Hoćeš li nešto pokušati?

66
00:08:52.785 --> 00:08:53.911
U redu.

67
00:08:57.206 --> 00:08:58.207
Učini to.

68
00:09:07.633 --> 00:09:10.428
Brže, brže!
-Vrti mi se!


69
00:09:18.853 --> 00:09:21.188
Ekipo, dođite u kuću. Večera.

70
00:09:22.982 --> 00:09:24.483
Ne želim ići u kuću.

71
00:09:24.567 --> 00:09:25.651
Hajde, ekipo.

72
00:09:27.695 --> 00:09:29.572
„Zavjetno utočište”

73
00:09:30.448 --> 00:09:32.617
Utrkujmo se!
-Čekajte!


74
00:09:38.873 --> 00:09:42.460
Zabavljaš se? U redu. Idemo.

75
00:09:42.543 --> 00:09:43.669
Moram piškiti.

76
00:09:43.753 --> 00:09:46.964
Budi brza. Ne želim ti rasrditi oca.

77
00:09:52.345 --> 00:09:56.140
Leti, leti, ptičice

78
00:09:56.224 --> 00:09:59.310
Preko moćnog mora

79
00:09:59.393 --> 00:10:01.729
Pjevaj, pjevaj, djevojčice

80
00:10:01.812 --> 00:10:04.982
Iz svega srca za mene

81
00:10:15.535 --> 00:10:17.245
Opa, lijepa si.

82
00:10:20.414 --> 00:10:23.251
Kako se zoveš, ljepoto? 
Ja sam Raylan.

83
00:10:25.002 --> 00:10:26.504
Baš me briga.

84
00:10:28.089 --> 00:10:30.550
Moram ići. Otac me čeka.

85
00:10:40.059 --> 00:10:43.521
Pucnem li prstima, odgrist će ti testise.

86
00:10:45.147 --> 00:10:47.525
Oho. U redu.

87
00:10:48.359 --> 00:10:51.654
Žao mi je ako sam te prestrašio.

88
00:10:52.238 --> 00:10:53.865
Tko kaže da jesi?

89
00:11:05.543 --> 00:11:07.044
Vidimo se.

90
00:11:07.628 --> 00:11:09.046
Dođi, Sjeno.

91
00:11:16.637 --> 00:11:18.014
Dobro si?

92
00:11:18.097 --> 00:11:20.850
Jesam. To je samo čudak.

93
00:11:20.933 --> 00:11:22.226
Da.

94
00:11:22.894 --> 00:11:25.563
Toga ovdje ne manjka.

95
00:11:39.535 --> 00:11:40.828
Slijedi ih.

96
00:11:51.047 --> 00:11:52.381
Hvala, Hernandezice.

97
00:11:53.174 --> 00:11:55.635
Danas smo se jako zabavile.

98
00:11:55.718 --> 00:11:58.054
Mogu je odvesti sljedeći tjedan
ako se slažete.


99
00:11:58.137 --> 00:12:01.182
Ne. Danas je bilo dovoljno.

100
00:12:06.812 --> 00:12:08.564
Gle, znam da me se ne tiče, ali...

101
00:12:08.648 --> 00:12:09.899
Imaš pravo.

102
00:12:10.775 --> 00:12:12.193
Ne tiče te se.

103
00:12:14.946 --> 00:12:16.614
Vi ste zločest čovjek.

104
00:12:19.575 --> 00:12:21.577
Čovjek koji je učinio grozote.

105
00:12:26.582 --> 00:12:29.001
Znam da to mislite.

106
00:12:29.085 --> 00:12:31.504
Kao i ja katkad za sebe.

107
00:12:33.548 --> 00:12:35.800
Rat nas sve promijeni.

108
00:12:36.551 --> 00:12:39.720
Nijedna duša ne vrati se čista iz njega.

109
00:12:41.264 --> 00:12:42.932
Ali nemojte da ona plaća za to.

110
00:12:46.978 --> 00:12:48.187
Hvala.

111
00:14:00.092 --> 00:14:04.805
Biste li maknuli vozilo s ceste? Ovo je...

112
00:14:08.017 --> 00:14:10.603
Ovo je jedina cesta do grada.

113
00:14:12.396 --> 00:14:14.482
Služila si?
-Jesam.


114
00:14:14.982 --> 00:14:16.275
I mi smo svi.

115
00:14:17.610 --> 00:14:19.570
Irak?
-Da.


116
00:14:19.904 --> 00:14:23.741
Nečasno otpušteni iz nečasnog rata.

117
00:14:25.910 --> 00:14:29.747
Rekao bih da nas
to čini časnima. Ti ne?

118
00:14:30.498 --> 00:14:31.707
Ne.

119
00:14:33.167 --> 00:14:36.462
Možete maknuti kamionet s ceste?

120
00:14:40.132 --> 00:14:42.093
Svakako, dušo.

121
00:14:42.176 --> 00:14:43.803
Što god ti želiš.

122
00:15:56.751 --> 00:15:59.712
Lekcije sljedeći mjesec.

123
00:16:00.129 --> 00:16:01.172
U redu.

124
00:16:02.173 --> 00:16:03.925
Sljedeće godine želim ići u školu.

125
00:16:05.384 --> 00:16:08.971
-Ovo je škola.
-U pravu, s djecom poput mene.


126
00:16:09.055 --> 00:16:10.640
Škola kod kuće je sigurnija.

127
00:16:10.723 --> 00:16:12.600
Ne želim biti sigurna.

128
00:16:12.683 --> 00:16:14.477
Želim biti normalna.

129
00:16:14.560 --> 00:16:17.230
Želim imati prijatelje, živjeti...
-Dosta!


130
00:16:18.022 --> 00:16:19.232
Dosta.

131
00:16:20.983 --> 00:16:25.196
Već sam jedanput izgubio kćer.
Neću izgubiti i tebe.


132
00:16:25.613 --> 00:16:27.365
Ali usamljena sam.

133
00:16:29.158 --> 00:16:31.786
Nemaš pojma što znači biti sam.

134
00:16:33.454 --> 00:16:34.997
Imaš mene.

135
00:16:38.876 --> 00:16:40.628
Ti nisi dovoljan.

136
00:17:37.018 --> 00:17:39.437
VAŠ NOVI DOM VAS ČEKA

137
00:17:43.149 --> 00:17:45.067
„Zavjetno utočište.

138
00:17:45.568 --> 00:17:47.570
Vaš novi dom vas čeka.”

139
00:19:03.980 --> 00:19:05.314
Sjeno?

140
00:19:48.858 --> 00:19:49.942
Sjeno?

141
00:24:39.649 --> 00:24:40.900
Sjeno.

142
00:24:47.240 --> 00:24:48.241
O, Bože.

143
00:24:50.826 --> 00:24:51.953
O, moj...

144
00:26:51.280 --> 00:26:53.574
Kutija! Odmah!

145
00:26:55.409 --> 00:26:56.452
Idi!

146
00:27:13.469 --> 00:27:14.971
Idi po curicu!

147
00:27:17.848 --> 00:27:18.808
PLIN

148
00:27:30.486 --> 00:27:31.821
Otvori vrata!

149
00:27:33.489 --> 00:27:34.699
Otvori!

150
00:30:00.720 --> 00:30:02.305
Koji kurac?

151
00:30:07.310 --> 00:30:08.853
Drži se, brate.

152
00:30:22.283 --> 00:30:23.993
Otvori čeljust.

153
00:30:24.577 --> 00:30:25.912
Ne miči se.

154
00:30:30.958 --> 00:30:32.043
Diši, brate.

155
00:30:50.353 --> 00:30:52.271
Tip je mornarički SEAL.

156
00:31:07.286 --> 00:31:09.413
Jebeni mrtvi SEAL, buraz.

157
00:32:10.141 --> 00:32:12.059
Bolje ti je da izađeš otamo, mala.

158
00:32:23.946 --> 00:32:25.865
On je dolje s tobom!

159
00:32:26.532 --> 00:32:28.618
Slijepi pizdun je ondje dolje!

160
00:32:46.677 --> 00:32:48.012
Zovi Raylana.

161
00:33:23.631 --> 00:33:25.925
Ta stara kutija gotovo je puna vode.

162
00:33:29.262 --> 00:33:31.472
Ako ti je draže vidjeti malu živu...

163
00:33:33.641 --> 00:33:35.560
Dođi ovamo.

164
00:33:38.521 --> 00:33:40.648
Misliš da se zajebavam s tobom?

165
00:33:44.569 --> 00:33:45.570
Ne.

166
00:33:48.030 --> 00:33:50.575
Žica pod naponom doći će do vode.

167
00:33:50.658 --> 00:33:52.493
Izađi ili ću je spržiti.

168
00:34:08.050 --> 00:34:09.510
Pametni pizdun.

169
00:34:10.428 --> 00:34:11.762
Bez oružja, ha?

170
00:34:13.097 --> 00:34:14.265
Nema problema.

171
00:36:49.795 --> 00:36:51.130
Žilav si.

172
00:36:52.882 --> 00:36:54.175
Ali gotov si.

173
00:37:06.354 --> 00:37:07.813
Koji kurac?

174
00:37:08.606 --> 00:37:09.649
Hej, buraz.

175
00:38:28.686 --> 00:38:30.062
Diši.

176
00:38:30.688 --> 00:38:32.064
Diši!

177
00:38:33.107 --> 00:38:34.525
Diši.

178
00:38:34.609 --> 00:38:35.860
Diši.

179
00:38:42.283 --> 00:38:44.243
Stari slijepac je ovo učinio?

180
00:38:44.327 --> 00:38:45.494
Aha.

181
00:38:48.748 --> 00:38:49.916
Idemo.

182
00:39:06.724 --> 00:39:08.100
Mogu hodati.

183
00:39:08.184 --> 00:39:09.685
Rekla sam da mogu hodati.

184
00:39:12.772 --> 00:39:14.023
Što se događa?

185
00:39:25.910 --> 00:39:27.203
Pazite na izlaze.

186
00:39:39.549 --> 00:39:41.217
Koji kurac?

187
00:40:09.036 --> 00:40:10.788
Još su ondje dolje.

188
00:40:41.152 --> 00:40:42.361
Što se događa?

189
00:40:43.863 --> 00:40:45.573
Tko su oni?
-Ne znam.


190
00:41:30.409 --> 00:41:32.495
Ne moraš se bojati, curice.

191
00:41:35.164 --> 00:41:38.167
Sve ovo je samo veliki nesporazum.

192
00:41:49.845 --> 00:41:51.973
Ne trebaš se mene bojati.

193
00:41:58.479 --> 00:42:00.773
Nego čovjeka pored sebe.

194
00:42:03.734 --> 00:42:05.653
Ja ti ne znam tko je on.

195
00:42:09.282 --> 00:42:10.616
Ali znam što nije.

196
00:42:19.584 --> 00:42:21.544
Da joj ja kažem ili ćeš ti?

197
00:42:28.467 --> 00:42:29.635
Dokrajči ga, buraz!

198
00:42:30.428 --> 00:42:31.429
Ne!

199
00:42:32.430 --> 00:42:33.347
Tata!

200
00:42:33.431 --> 00:42:35.349
Tata, probudi se!
-Baš si mustra.


201
00:42:36.809 --> 00:42:38.060
Pusti me!

202
00:42:40.021 --> 00:42:41.230
Dođi.

203
00:42:42.231 --> 00:42:43.232
Ne, u redu je.

204
00:42:47.195 --> 00:42:50.364
Da. Tako. Tako.

205
00:42:51.616 --> 00:42:53.743
Doista me se ne sjećaš, je li?

206
00:42:55.536 --> 00:42:57.038
Možda ti ovo pomogne.

207
00:43:07.548 --> 00:43:08.633
Vidiš?

208
00:43:13.721 --> 00:43:14.805
Što...

209
00:43:17.850 --> 00:43:20.019
Prije mnogo godina
u kući nam je izbio požar.


210
00:43:20.770 --> 00:43:22.897
Murja je okrivila mene.

211
00:43:22.980 --> 00:43:26.442
Proveo sam osam godina u zatvoru
pitajući se hoću li te opet vidjeti.


212
00:43:30.613 --> 00:43:33.324
Nisam znao ni jesi
li li živa ili mrtva.

213
00:43:37.662 --> 00:43:42.458
Ovaj gad te pronašao
i zadržao te za sebe.


214
00:43:44.126 --> 00:43:45.503
Mjesne vijesti.

215
00:43:45.586 --> 00:43:49.215
Jutros se u Detroitu
zapalio labos za meth.


216
00:43:49.298 --> 00:43:52.051
Policija je uhitila glavnog sumnjivca.

217
00:43:52.134 --> 00:43:54.929
Čovjek je uhićen i možda ga optuže

218
00:43:55.012 --> 00:43:58.182
za brojne zločine
počinjene proteklih godina.


219
00:43:58.266 --> 00:44:01.435
Nemaš pojma koliko sam
čekao ovaj trenutak.


220
00:44:17.493 --> 00:44:18.744
Je li te ozlijedio?

221
00:44:21.289 --> 00:44:24.542
Ali ukrao mi te je
i sada mora umrijeti. Shvaćaš?


222
00:44:27.086 --> 00:44:28.087
Ubij ga.

223
00:44:28.713 --> 00:44:30.590
Ne!
-Koji kurac radiš?


224
00:44:31.007 --> 00:44:33.551
Ne pred mojim djetetom. 
Obavi to vani.

225
00:44:39.181 --> 00:44:42.435
Probudi se, pizdune slijepi!

226
00:44:45.229 --> 00:44:46.147
Jebemti!

227
00:45:08.336 --> 00:45:10.087
Jebena kukavica.

228
00:45:16.844 --> 00:45:20.264
Odvedi je u kamionet
dok ja lovim ovog pizduna. Idemo.


229
00:45:26.729 --> 00:45:28.773
Pusti me!
-Što nije u redu s tobom?


230
00:45:29.482 --> 00:45:30.858
Želiš li ići kući, jebote?

231
00:45:56.968 --> 00:45:58.678
Nije me briga tko si.

232
00:45:58.761 --> 00:46:00.888
Naučit ću te ponašanju.

233
00:46:01.556 --> 00:46:03.391
Nezahvalna mala kučko.

234
00:46:11.607 --> 00:46:12.650
Ne!

235
00:46:22.451 --> 00:46:23.452
Ne!

236
00:46:31.752 --> 00:46:32.670
Stani.

237
00:46:33.671 --> 00:46:34.547
Molim te!

238
00:46:35.590 --> 00:46:36.924
Prestani!

239
00:46:52.440 --> 00:46:54.025
Kreni. Idemo.

240
00:46:54.108 --> 00:46:56.194
Kreni! Odmah!

241
00:47:23.971 --> 00:47:25.223
Kreni!

242
00:47:38.069 --> 00:47:39.320
Žao mi je, čovječe.

243
00:47:42.740 --> 00:47:46.244
Vratio se u kuću.
-Znam. Želi da ga slijedimo.


244
00:47:48.746 --> 00:47:50.706
Dosta je ovih smiješnih igrica.

245
00:48:08.349 --> 00:48:09.684
To je njegova jakna.

246
00:48:11.936 --> 00:48:14.063
Bravo. Bravo!

247
00:48:16.065 --> 00:48:18.568
Čekaj. Stani.

248
00:48:20.695 --> 00:48:23.155
Je li istina?
-Kreni.


